Class SubscriptionObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.SubscriptionObserver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observers.IObserver, Observers.ISubscriptionObserver
    public class SubscriptionObserver extends java.lang.Object implements Observers.ISubscriptionObserver
    Provides a base class implementation of the ISubscriptionObserver interface, making private implementation of interface methods optional. The base implementation of each interface method does nothing.
